data.model

Class NavigationItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.model.IdentifiableItem
      • data.model.BaseItem
        • data.model.NavigationItem

  • public class NavigationItem
extends BaseItem
    Represents one item in the Arcadoid front-end navigation. If can be used to show specific subitems, or to show games that match one or several tags.
    Author:
    Thomas Debouverie
